Defines the single-source-of-truth agent-facing contract string for the `ctx-scan` binary, exposed as `pub const CONTRACT: &str`.

The string's content is load-bearing: it's assembled into the tool-contract block in `CLAUDE.md`/`README.md`, and a `contracts` battery check fails if those generated docs drift from this literal. Editing this string requires regenerating those docs to keep the check passing — the file itself has no logic, only the constant.